import React from "react";
import {
  Accordion,
  AccordionButton,
  AccordionIcon,
  AccordionItem,
  AccordionPanel,
  Box,
  HStack,
  Icon,
  Path,
  Text,
} from "native-base";

export default function SidebarItems() {
  return (
    <Box mt={12}>
      <Accordion>
        <AccordionItem>
          <AccordionButton _expanded={{ backgroundColor: "orange.3" }}>
            <HStack ml={2} space={4}>
              <Icon viewBox="0 0 50 50" color="#5F72E4">
                <Path d="M 24.962891 1.0546875 A 1.0001 1.0001 0 0 0 24.384766 1.2636719 L 1.3847656 19.210938 A 1.0005659 1.0005659 0 1 0 2.6152344 20.789062 L 4 19.708984 L 4 46 A 1.0001 1.0001 0 0 0 5 47 L 18.832031 47 A 1.0001 1.0001 0 0 0 19.158203 47 L 30.832031 47 A 1.0001 1.0001 0 0 0 31.158203 47 L 45 47 A 1.0001 1.0001 0 0 0 46 46 L 46 19.708984 L 47.384766 20.789062 A 1.0005657 1.0005657 0 1 0 48.615234 19.210938 L 41 13.269531 L 41 6 L 35 6 L 35 8.5859375 L 25.615234 1.2636719 A 1.0001 1.0001 0 0 0 24.962891 1.0546875 z M 25 3.3222656 L 44 18.148438 L 44 45 L 32 45 L 32 26 L 18 26 L 18 45 L 6 45 L 6 18.148438 L 25 3.3222656 z M 37 8 L 39 8 L 39 11.708984 L 37 10.146484 L 37 8 z M 20 28 L 30 28 L 30 45 L 20 45 L 20 28 z" />
              </Icon>
              <Text pt={1} fontWeight={500} fontFamily="sans-serif">
                Dashboards
              </Text>
            </HStack>
            <AccordionIcon />
          </AccordionButton>
          <AccordionPanel>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do
            eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim
            ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut
            aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
          </AccordionPanel>
        </AccordionItem>
      </Accordion>
    </Box>
  );
}
